ygData.msgSnippet: Well met, Kaolas!  It is I, Shaleena the huntress.  Glad to hear you are still in good health and spirit! To the rest of you, I am Shaleena, the Wood elven
ygData.messageBody:
Well met, Kaolas! It is I, Shaleena the huntress. Glad to hear you are still
in good health and spirit!

To the rest of you, I am Shaleena, the Wood elven huntress, and woe betide
those who think they can do harm to my home. To those who love the woods,
and help protect them, I am ever a steadfast ally, and have been known many
times to stand ground to hack down Orcen and goblin kin to protect a child
of the forest who has gotten in over their heads.



At 11:40 AM 4/5/99 -0500, you wrote:
>>From: "Mark Bourland" <bourland@...>
>>
>>Hail to all.
>>I am Kaolas the Halfelven.
>>I reside, more often than not, in or around Kelethin. Call on me in need.
>>
>>
